cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "CAVE Sensory Reweighting (cave-frf)"
message: >-
  If you use this pipeline in published work, please cite the
  foundational methodology (Hwang et al. 2014) and the
  dissertation (Vanderlinde dos Santos 2019) alongside this
  repository.
type: software
