    orcid: ""  # add Jaclyn's ORCID here if available
keywords:
  - concussion
  - sensory reweighting
  - postural control
  - frequency response function
  - mTBI
  - balance
  - multisensory fusion
abstract: >-
  Python pipeline computing frequency response function
  (gain, phase, coherence) and per-trial summary metrics for
  postural sway in response to a sum-of-sines visual
  perturbation. Built for the CAVE Adult Stimulus Factor
  study (Control vs Concussion, Acute / SubAcute / Chronic
  timepoints, Standing and Walking conditions). Continues
  the sensory-reweighting research line of Hwang et al. 2014
  and Vanderlinde dos Santos 2019.
